Job Description:
Meeting with business units and clients to determine and capture detailed requirements;
Clarifying a system specification, understanding work practices and the nature of the business of the requestor and stakeholders;
Planning project timelines;
Creating high-level implementation plans when required;
Developing agreed solutions and implementing new systems;
Presenting solutions in written or oral reports;
White-boarding complete or partial solutions;
Creating project deliverables;
Designing, installing, integrating, testing, and monitoring new systems;
